{"tid":2493745,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《南早》：國安署徵用港島太平洋酒店","createTime":"2021-04-18T06:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T06:52:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"90c90bbad31b9005a759552fab6e3698607d43c1","tid":2493745,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:50:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210418/BJ3YRHM7HVDX5DENIOQV7T3OTY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210418%2FBJ3YRHM7HVDX5DENIOQV7T3OTY%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RIOqxcwteoRdaW8BGlJRIvY%3D&h=8125098f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210418%2FBJ3YRHM7HVDX5DENIOQV7T3OTY%2F&h=8d6ad266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210418/BJ3YRHM7HVDX5DENIOQV7T3OTY/</a><br />\n<br />\n《南早》：國安署徵用港島太平洋酒店<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VQ-j3J4XAOxlussy16NVxOe2nXU=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LJ34GOCZDZB5TMUCHVQ5FLNGHE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVQ-j3J4XAOxlussy16NVxOe2nXU%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLJ34GOCZDZB5TMUCHVQ5FLNGHE.jpg&h=19fa469a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■國安公署徵用的港島太平洋酒店位於中聯辦大樓附近。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】《南華早報》引述消息人士報道，中央駐港國安公署已徵用港島太平洋酒店作辦公大樓，酒店地點鄰近西營盤的中聯辦大樓，是繼去年7月徵用香港中旅集團旗下銅鑼灣維景酒店後，再度使用酒店作國安基地，並擴張辦公室規模。<br />\n<br />\n港島太平洋酒店由信和集團營運，早前曾被列入旅發局「賞你住」參與酒店名單之一，但上星期突然傳出暫停營業消息，酒店網頁及社交平台專頁亦已關閉。信和集團早前承認，該酒店已與一機構落實批量出租安排，需暫停營運以作準備及調整，惟未有透露租用者身份。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正式基地稍後拍板<br />\n<br />\n《南早》報道，租用者為中央駐港國安公署，酒店位置與中聯辦大樓僅一街之隔，三分鐘車程即可到達。酒店於2018年底曾翻新，樓高29層，停運前提供逾300間客房，現正進行改裝工程。國安公署和酒店的租約只會維持一段時間（some period），現正位於銅鑼灣維景酒店的國安公署辦公室亦只屬臨時性質，正式基地將於稍後拍板。<br />\n<br />\n新一份財政預算案。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"5ec74b0e80a3652526f230054f6562552f169dc6","tid":2493745,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:52:23.000Z","msg":"準備打地主<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}